author: spepping
msg: Prepare for new hyphenation pattern files, which do not have their own classes and instead use the default classes in FOP. Modified the build process to a forked java task, in order to be able to set a larger stack size for the compilation of the large number of classes. Added an ant task to generate a new default classes file, to be used with an update of the Unicode Character Database.
